{
  "stem": "17426.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 106.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then in Kowal, which is another town north of Turek, there were other trucks that joined us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when we came to the camp, we were a Kolonie of 16, 18 trucks.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were 1,040 people delivered to that one school house.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was in fenced.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This was with guards, and this was with gates.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there were dogs that escorted us in a no-describable hostile manner to our barracks.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The barracks were-- we were in the school house and one school room.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Which ordinarily was built for 40-- 30, 40 students at most-- we was 80 sleeping in this house, in this particular room.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And our quarters that we slept on were simple shelves, just shelves, four stories high, four levels high.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And as we were driven into this room for that my father and I were to be, we were trying to find a spot on these shelves.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was-- it was precious.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Everyone ran to put his little rucksack that he had with him, this little satchel, so that he could claim this spot.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was nothing on the higher shelf.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had to settle for the floor shelf.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that was the most undesirable spot to have because you had to go down on your knees.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You had to bend down with your head in order to slide in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And you slid in on your neck and on your ankles, on your elbows, and on your knees.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And so we made our home for a year in Steineck on this floor.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the-- soon we were plagued by vermin, by lice, by fleas, in such a manner that's hard to describe.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We could-- in time, they grow so many of them that we could take them out in fists off the blankets.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
